urn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614997\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oix1665702652724.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oix1665702652724.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oix1665702652724.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oix1665702652724\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines how the layout state for forms and grid widgets is stored. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">PROCESS</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">COMPONENT</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">INSTANCE</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oix1665702652724__section_w4290ab1b5b1_w4291ab1b5_w4292ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">PROCESS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__2\">\n Keeps layout state information while the process is active, but does not write it to the Registry. The internal name used is <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">COMPONENT</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__2\">\n Writes layout state information to the Registry under the name <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">INSTANCE</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11645e1_d11646e1_d11647e1__entry__2\">\n Writes layout state information to the Registry under the name <var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>.\n <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"oix1665702652724__note_w4293ab1b5b1b1b3b7b5b3b5_w4294ab1b5b1b1b3b7b5b3_w4295ab1b5b1b1b3b7b5_w4296ab1b5b1b1b3b7_w4297ab1b5b1b1b3_w4298ab1b5b1b1_w4299ab1b5b1_w4300ab1b5_w4301ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> State information is stored only if user-defined instance names have been used. It is not stored if the instance name has been generated by Uniface, such as 00001111.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oix1665702652724__section_enn_svw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d522950e151\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"oix1665702652724__table_d11648e1_d11649e1_d11650e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Keep Layout State</span> must\n                        be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oix1665702652724__section_kg4_5vw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d522950e202\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oix1665702652724__p_d100046e1_d100047e1_d100048e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Keep Layout State</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> for a Form, but <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Layout State Storage</span> is\n            not defined, Uniface behaves as if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Layout State Storage</span> is set to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Component</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oix1665702652724__p_d100049e1_d100050e1_d100051e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Keep Layout State</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code> for a Form, but <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> for a Grid in the Form,\n            the Grid layout state is stored at the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Instance</code> level in the Registry,\n            but only if the instance name has not been generated by Uniface.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oix1665702652724__section_uft_xvw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d522950e241\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"oix1665702652724__ul_m5g_yvw_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oix1665702652724__li_d40445e1_d40446e1_d40447e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oix1665702652724__li_d40448e1_d40449e1_d40450e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"clg1695282025414.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/clg1695282025414.html\" title=\"The egrid widget displays data in a tabular format, in which the rows are occurrences of an entity and the columns are fields. It is an entity-level widget that is only applicable to form components.\">egrid (Grid)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eao1665702652656.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keep Layout State (KeepLayout)</a><p>Window property that controls whether layout information is kept. Values are True (default) or False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614997\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614997\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Layout State Storage (LAYOUTSTORAGE) Determines how the layout state for forms and grid widgets is stored. Valid values are PROCESS , COMPONENT , or INSTANCE . Value Description PROCESS Keeps layout state information while the process is active, but does not write it to the Registry. The internal name used is ComponentName / InstanceName . COMPONENT Writes layout state information to the Registry under the name ComponentName INSTANCE Writes layout state information to the Registry under the name ComponentName / InstanceName . Note: State information is stored only if user-defined instance names have been used. It is not stored if the instance name has been generated by Uniface, such as 00001111. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? Yes Dependencies: Keep Layout State must be True . Description If Keep Layout State is True for a Form, but Layout State Storage is not defined, Uniface behaves as if Layout State Storage is set to Component . If Keep Layout State is False for a Form, but True for a Grid in the Form, the Grid layout state is stored at the Instance level in the Registry, but only if the instance name has not been generated by Uniface. Applies to Form egrid (Grid) Related Links Keep Layout State (KeepLayout) Window property that controls whether layout information is kept. Values are True (default) or False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}